Map:
  plots singular data point of (as one source is shown at a time)
  - ideally, size increase with pollution increase and color turns red for higher pollution.
  
Selectors:
 - Selects what data to plot from dataset
 - Only ONE selector can be plotted at a time.
 
 Year Slider:
  - Changes the date of the dot plotted on the map. 

Plot:
 - Shows long term trend of data (graphs ALL of the given data for the selector
  - [ALL DATA throught ALL YEARS on that pollution element])
 - For now, we only have bar charts.
 - Ideally, they could select multiple graph types (line plot/ bar chart / etc...)
 
 Is a Web APP w/ touch screen support.
 
 Try to host it in cloud.
